OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779311467
OL,3,CRussian jets 'dangerously' intercepted
OL,4,CRAF spy plane above Black Sea
OL,6,FTwo Russian jets "repeatedly and
OL,7,Fdangerously" intercepted an RAF spy
OL,8,Fplane above the Black Sea, the
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) has said.
OL,11,FA Russian Su-35 jet flew so close to
OL,12,Fthe British reconnaissance aircraft
OL,13,Fthat it triggered its emergency
OL,14,Fsystems, including disabling the
OL,15,Fautopilot.
OL,17,FOne of the nation's Su-27s also flew
OL,18,Fsix metres from the unarmed Rivet
OL,19,FJoint's nose and carried out six
OL,20,Fpasses in front.
OL,26,@nD@ROUoD@LO]
