PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779311467
OL,3,CRussian jets 'dangerously' intercepted
OL,4,CRAF spy plane above Black Sea
OL,6,FIt is the most dangerous Russian
OL,7,Faction against a British Rivet Joint
OL,8,Faircraft since a plane fired a missile
OL,9,Fover the Black Sea in 2022, the MoD
OL,10,Fsaid when it revealed the
OL,11,Finterceptions on Wednesday.
OL,13,FThis comes after the Defence
OL,14,FSecretary, John Healey, in April
OL,15,Frevealed that the UK had tracked three
OL,16,FRussian submarines that loitered over
OL,17,Fcritical undersea infrastructure in
OL,18,Fthe North Atlantic for a month before
OL,19,Fretreating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
