OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779311467
OL,3,CRussian jets 'dangerously' intercepted
OL,4,CRAF spy plane above Black Sea
OL,6,FAfter the airborne interception,
OL,7,FHealey said in a statement: "This
OL,8,Fincident is another example of
OL,9,Fdangerous and unacceptable behaviour
OL,10,Fby Russian pilots, towards an unarmed
OL,11,Faircraft operating in international
OL,12,Fairspace.
OL,14,F"These actions create a serious risk
OL,15,Fof accidents and potential escalation."
OL,26,@oD@]OUvD@AOUwD@gO]
