OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779311467
OL,3,CRussian jets 'dangerously' intercepted
OL,4,CRAF spy plane above Black Sea
OL,6,FThe Rivet Joint was conducting a
OL,7,Froutine flight in international
OL,8,Fairspace above the Black Sea as part
OL,9,Fof the UK's work with allies to
OL,10,F"secure Nato's eastern flank", the MoD
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe aircraft uses advanced sensors for
OL,19,Felectronic surveillance.
