OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779311467
OL,3,CRussian jets 'dangerously' intercepted
OL,4,CRAF spy plane above Black Sea
OL,6,FHealey added: "I would like to pay
OL,7,Ftribute to the outstanding
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and bravery of the RAF
OL,9,Fcrew who continued with their mission
OL,10,Fdespite these dangerous actions.
OL,12,F"Let me be very clear: This incident
OL,13,Fwill not deter the UK's commitment to
OL,14,Fdefend Nato, our allies and our
OL,15,Finterests from Russian aggression."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
